==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Denouncement
<hw>De*nounce"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. OF.
<ets>denoncement</ets>.]</ety> <def>Solemn, official, or menacing
announcement; denunciation.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>False is the reply of Cain, upon the <qex>denouncement</qex> of
his curse.</q> <rj><qau>Sir T. Browne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Denouncer</ent>⟦br⟧
